+        // -> conditional commitCrime(OT_Theft) with LOS/awareness witness detection + bounty. This is
+        // MechanicsManager::itemTaken, which vanilla invokes from ContainerWindow's take handlers
+        // (Container/InventoryItemModel::onTakeItem) but which the DS companion's Lua moveInto() take
+        // path never touches. Global-only (it mutates world crime state). Corpse-looting must be excluded
